debug_hart_halted.name: debug_hart_halted
debug_hart_halted.description: Debug ROM Causes hart to write its hartID here when it is in Debug Mode.

debug_hart_going.name: debug_hart_going
debug_hart_going.description: Debug ROM causes hart to write 0 here when it begins executing Debug Mode instructions.

debug_hart_resuming.name: debug_hart_resuming
debug_hart_resuming.description: Debug ROM causes hart to write its hartID here when it leaves Debug Mode.

debug_hart_exception.name: debug_hart_exception
debug_hart_exception.description: Debug ROM causes hart to write 0 here if it gets an exception in Debug Mode.

debug_data_0.name: debug_data_0
debug_data_0.groupDesc: Data used to communicate with Debug Module

debug_progbuf_0.name: debug_progbuf_0
debug_progbuf_0.groupDesc: Program buffer used to communicate with Debug Module

debug_whereto.name: debug_whereto
debug_whereto.description: Instruction filled in by Debug Module to control hart in Debug Mode

debug_flags_$i.name: debug_flags_$i
debug_flags_$i.groupDesc: Memory region used to control hart going/resuming in Debug Mode
